── greet ──────────────────────────
│ name → message
│
│ Greet the person by name.
│ Produce a friendly hello message.
│
│ ✓ message is a single sentence
│ ✓ message contains the name
──────────────────────────────────

── wrap ───────────────────────────
│ greet.message → text, emoji
│
│ Take the greeting and wrap it
│ with an appropriate emoji.
│
│ ✓ text equals the original message
│ ✓ emoji is a single unicode emoji
──────────────────────────────────
